A dramatic, painterly instant card illustration depicting a battle-hardened warrior, weathered and stained with ale, raising a toast with a massive, ancient tankard overflowing with bubbling crimson liquid. Around him, dozens of tiny, fiery red dwarf creatures swarm and charge, echoing the action, in a dynamic, slightly chaotic scene with a gritty, old-world aesthetic, reminiscent of a medieval tavern brawl, art old.